Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Katerina, poklyanis na svyatoy ikone! Swear it, Katerina! - Act One
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Ay, Ay - Act One
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Ay! - Act One
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Chego stoite? -What are you standing around for? - Act One
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Spat' pora -Time for bed - Act One

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Kto eto, kto, kto stuchit? -Who is it, who's knocking? - Act One

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Chto znachit' starost' -This is what it means to be old - Act Two

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Gribke vkusnye -The mushrooms are tasty - Act Two
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Vidno, skoro uzh zarya -See, the dawn's already breaking - Act Two

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Interlude - Act Two
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Sergey, Seryozha - Act Two

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Slushay, Sergey, Sergey -Listen, Sergey, Sergey - Act Two
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Nesi v pogreb -Take him to the cellar - Act Two

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: U menya byla kuma, pit' lyubila bez uma -I once had a grandmother who drank like crazy - Act Three
Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Sozdan politseysky byl vo vremya ono -The police were formed in days of old - Act Three

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Shto takoe? -What is it? - Act Three

Shostakovich: Katerina Ismailova: Ey vy, step neobyatnye -Oh, you endless steppes - Act Four
